Template: kiosk-user/username
Type: string
Description: Username:
 User to run kiosk application as (will be created if it doesn't exist).
 .
 Warning: Existing user's files will be modified.

Template: kiosk-user/username_error
Type: error
Description: Invalid username.
 The username that was entered is invalid.

Template: kiosk-user/execpath
Type: string
Description: Application path:
 Path to executable to run as kiosk application.

Template: kiosk-user/execpath_error
Type: error
Description: Invalid application path.
 The given path is incorrect, or the file is not executable.

Template: kiosk-user/execargs
Type: string
Description: Application arguments:
 Command-line arguments to pass to the application.

Template: kiosk-user/options
Type: multiselect
Choices: All options, ${options}

Template: kiosk-user/disable_titlebar
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: for internal use

Template: kiosk-user/disable_blanking
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: for internal use

Template: kiosk-user/hide_cursor
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: for internal use

Template: kiosk-user/use_cursor
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: for internal use
